*******************
OPERATIONS
*******************
GET index (Operations list)

http://laravel-smartgit/api/operations
*******************
GET show (Show operation)

http://laravel-smartgit/api/operations/{operation}
*******************
POST store (Store operation)

http://laravel-smartgit/api/operations

HEADERS
Content-Type application/json

BODY
{
    "sum" : 2000,
    "category_id" : 1,
    "description" : "Тест создание операции по API"
}

required fields: sum, category_id

sum - сумма операции;
category_id - id категории;
description - описание операции;
*******************
PUT update (Update operation)

http://laravel-smartgit/api/operations/{operation}

HEADERS
Content-Type application/json

BODY
{
    "sum" : 2000,
    "category_id" : 1,
    "description" : "Тест редактирования операции по API"
}

required fields: sum, category_id

sum - сумма операции;
category_id - id категории;
description - описание операции;
api_token - api токен пользователя;
*******************
DELETE destroy (Destroy operation)

http://laravel-smartgit/api/operations/{operation}